PrecisReappointment of GERALDINE VAN BIBBER of Whitehorse, Yukon Territory, to be Administrator of the Yukon Territory to execute the office and functions of the Commissioner during his absence or illness or other inability or when the office of Commissioner is vacant, for a term of three years.
